\id JOS Kyaka Enga Shorter Bible, SF codes August 20, 93 
\h JOSUA 
\toc1 JOSUA 
\toc2 Josua 
\toc3 Jos 
\mt1 JOSUA  
\ip Buku dake Josua lenge dokona Isaraele wambu dupwame yuu Kenane range dupwa pyao ralipala yuu nyiyami dokona arome pii pyasi palamo. Dopa piyaminyi dokopa akali Josua lenge dokome baa Isaraele wambu dupwa peparae iso kareya. Pii liti rema ingyuo pyasi palamo.  
\io1 \bk 1. Rombo 1-12 \bk*Isaraele wambu dupwa ipwa Jotane yalo pao yuu Kenane pyao ralipala nyiyami.  
\io1 \bk 2. Rombo 13-22 \bk*Yuu Kenane anamasi minyuo nyuo kunjo liti pyuo rara akalisa ipisu lama dusipana mokwa soo nyuo piyami letamo.  
\io1 \bk 3. Rombo 23-24 \bk*Josua kumalana repe ingiyamo dokopa kanju lao mondo lao pyuo karena lao wambu dupwa lamaiya. Yuu lamana pii doko leyamo dokopa yuu Sikeme dokona Isaraele wambu dupwa kana minyuo Anatu keta lalu lao leyami.  
\c 1  
\s1 Anatumi Josua Kando Yuu Kenane Doko Pyao Wini Pira Lao Lamaiya  
\p
\v 1 Kamongona kendemande akali Mosese kumapeyamo dokopa enakana Mosesena nyiso yulu pingi akali Nanena ikinyingi Josua doko kando Kamongome pii lamaiya.  
\v 2 Baame lamaiyuo lao, Nambana kendemande akali Mosese doko kumapya dokona epapu rapa rapa pipala embape dee Isaraele wambu peparaepe ipwa Jotane doko yalo pao yuu nambame nakama mailyunu dokona sukusa pali pupwape.  
\v 3 Mosese lamaiyunuli pyuo nakama kimbu kimbu kalyuo eparami yuu peparae embape nambana wambu dupwanape lao retakayo, leya.  
\v 4 Nakamana yuu liti make doko yuu muiyane dokona pisipala pao yuu Lepanone kyau dupwana suu lara. Dee ipwa andake Yuporisa lenge dokona piso pao Itai wambunya yuu peparaena piso pao neta anda pao yalyingi dorename ipwa kota pete andake Metitaraniane lenge dokona pao nakamana lili ingyara.  
\v 5 Josua emba lete kararene yuu gii dusipana mendemepe emba nyuo isa palyuo wini pira ingya nalyamo. Namba Mosese keta pyakamyuo kareyonoli pyuo emba keta dopako pyakao kararo. Dee yuu peparae namba emba role karo emba yaki nyuo kaeyaronde daa.  
\v 6 Embame mona kumapala yulu dokona pilyuŋu lao suu pyao kandokondali pyuo poraiyuo pepe. Dokona lao nambame nakamana rora ambasu dupwa keta yuu mairu lao lalu lao leyono dokona nakama palyuo kararaminyi dokopa emba wambu dapwana mupwa ingyuo iso karare.  
\v 7 Dokona kando mona kumapala porai ingyuo karo nambana kendemande akali Moseseme Mawa Pii emba jiya dusipa peparae warombo soo minyuo pyuo karape. Mawa Pii peparae dupwana mende yaki nyii napipi. Dopa pyuo karo dokopa kata peparae papirinyi dupwana kapa ingyara.  
\v 8 Embame Mawa Pii buku doko kambunya lao lao pyuo karape. Yuu peparae kukwa korakama lao mana nyepala pii dokona pyasi palamo dusipa peparae suu pyanyi pyano piso dokopa warombo sepe. Dokopa emba au pyuo keyange ingyuo elyape keta pare.  
\v 9 Nambame emba kando, Mona kumapala porai ingyuo yulu dokona kandokondali pyuo karape lao mana langiyu kande. Dokona lao namba embena Kamongo Anatu emba anja panda parene dupwana role pyapeta paramba dokona paka nao mona nemba nao poraiyuo karape, lao Kamongome leya.   
\s1 Josuame Wambu Dupwa Dopa Pinya Lao Mana Lamaiya  
\p
\v 10 Dokopa Josuame akali mupwa dupwame wambu palyuo petaminyi yuu dokona papyuo pii lamainya lao lamaiyuo,  
\v 11 Yuu gii rema paparamopa ipwa Jotane doko yalo nakamana Kamongo Anatu dokome yuu jipyamo dokona karala paramaŋa dokona nenge lapo rapa rapa pinya lena leya.   
\p
\v 12 Josuame akali Urupene rarape Gatena rarape dee akali Manasana rara pingyasi pakipi lamaiyuo lao,  
\v 13 Kamongona kendemande akali Mosese dokome nakama langiya kande. Doko nakamana Kamongo Anatu dokome ipwa Jotane epenge yuu neta pyakalyingi dorena nakama rangena ingyara lao jeraŋa, leya.  
\v 14-15 Nakamana enda wanepe dee mena bulamakaope dupwa dae kararaminyipa nakamana yanda singi dupwa yanda pingi bange dupwa minyuo nakamana Isaraele yango dupwa enakao epena lapala nakama nyiso wambo parami. Pao nakamana Kamongo Anatu dokome ipwa Jotane epenge yuu neta anda pao yalyingi dorena maipyamo dokona kapa pao kararami doko kandapala kaeyarami. Kapa kareyami kande doko kandapala Isaraele rara dupwa peparae nakama kapu kyuo epo ipa Jotane neta epenge yuu dorename akali Moseseme nakamba yuu rangena lao jiyamo dokona palyuo kararami, leya.   
\p
\v 16 Leyamo dokopa nakamame Josua isingi lamaiyuo lao, Embame pii peparae namwa langilinyili pyuo pirama dee embame anja pupwa larenele pyuo parama.  
\v 17 Namwame yuu peparae Mosesena pii warombo singi dokoko suu pyao embena pii warombo serama. Dokona embena Kamongo Anatu Mosese role karenge dokoko suu pyao emba keta role pyao karena.  
\v 18 Namwana wambu dupwana mendeme embena yulu dupwana pisalya pisana pyuo dee embena pii larene dupwana lapo kamba lao pirami dupwa pyao kumakarama. Dokona mona kumapala porai ingyuo yulu doko kandokondali pyuo pyuo karape, leyami.   
\c 2  
\s1 Josuame Akali Lama Yalu Pyuo Yuu Jereko Doko Kandala Pena Leya  
\p
\v 1 Dokopa Josuame akali lama yuu Akasia wambu palyuo paleyaminyi dokona yaki nyuo yuu Kenane doko yalu pyuo kandala pena leya. Yuu Kenane doko kando nyepala yuu taone andake mende Jereko lenge doko angingyuo poraiyuo kandena leya. Nakamba yuu Jereko dokona epo yuu gii kukwa dokopa enda pamuku mende kingi Oreapa lenge dokona anda pali peyambi.  
\v 2 Kukwa dokopa Isaraele akali lapome yuu doko yalu pyuo kandala imi leyaminyipa Jereko kiŋi dokome siya.  
\v 3 Sepala dokona lao baame Oreapa keta pii nembapala lao, Akali embena anda petambinyi dolapome yuu dake peparae yalu pyuo kandala imbi. Dokona nakamba kamanda lanyuo ipupi, leya.   
\p
\v 4-6 Leyamo dokopa enda dokome isingi lao, Kinyi akali lapo nambana anda iminyipape nakamba anja range lao namba see nalyo. Doko nakamba neta anda pupyamopa yuu taone kambu kii doko palyapa naminyipa nambana anda yaki nyuo pumbi. Doko anja pelyambinyi lao piso see napu. Embame pumbinyi dokona waiya lao moko minyuo pare ramo doko kapa kando nyere, leya. (Enda Oreapame akali dolapo anda ketae dorena lanyuo papala puu yaki dopale reteya dokona minyalyapala yalu pyuo koko petena leya.)  
\v 7 Dokopa kiŋinya akali lapo yuu taone doko yaki nyuo papeyami dokopa kambu kii doko paleya. Nakama Isaraele akali lama yalu pyuo yuu waa kandala epeyambi dolapo koto pao ama nanesa wakasa kata ipwa Jotane yalo penge dokona peyami.\fig Yuu Kenane doko kando nyepala yuu taone andake mende Jereko lenge doko angingyuo poraiyuo kandena leya.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="2:1" \fig*   
\p
\v 8 Yuu gii kukwa dokopa akali dolapo luu palipa nayambinyipa enda Oreapa doko anda ketae dokona peya.  
\v 9 Papala nakamba lamaiyuo lao, Kamongo dokome yuu dake nakamba jipyamo doko namba silyu. Doko yuu dakena range wambu peparae dupwa nakamba kando pakalyaminyi.  
\v 10 Nakama yuu Isipi yaki nyuo epeyaminyipa Kamongo dokome ipwa Kota Kone lenge doko soko rali piyamopa nakama dokona kata siyamo epeyami doko namwa siyama. Dee ipwa Jotane epenge yuu neta pyakalyingi dorena Amote akali kiŋi lama kingi Sayone dee Oke lenge dolapo pyao kumakayami doko namwa siyamako.  
\v 11 Namwa doko siyama dokopa aopa pakayama. Nakama ama porai ingilyaminyi leyami doko sepala namwana porai renge doko isa puu pao peya. Nakamana Kamongo Anatu doko yake panda ketae dokona baako karenge dee isa yuu pandape peparaena baako karenge.  
\v 12 Epapu banya kingi lao, nambame nakamba anjiki pyuo rapu pilyu doko suu pyao nakambame nambana ree palu dupwa anjiki pyuo rapu pyakaramba lao lalu lao lalapape. Dee nambame nakamba kinyi angiŋi lao suu pyaroleŋe yulu mende pyuo lasaka pipwape.  
\v 13 Pipala nambana anyipi rakanepe kakingipi pemalengepe dee dupwana ree palu peparaepe kyawa lete nyakaramaŋa lao namba kando lalu lao lalapape. Dee namwa pyao kumakana lao kyawa yaki nyii nalapape, leya.   
\p
\v 14 Leyamo dokopa akali dolapome enda doko lamaiyuo lao, Namwa letamanuli pyuo pii narama ramo doko namwana Anatu dokome namwa pyao kumakana. Nambwa yulu pimbwano doko embame mendali lamai nare ramo doko Kamongome yuu dake namwa jeramo dokopa emba poraiyuo rapu pyuo kararama lao lalu lao letambano, leyambi.   
\p
\v 15 Enda Oreapa banya anda doko pyuo pao yuu taone dokona kana kame dokona suu lasindena palenge. Dokome akali dolapo puu karapala windowa kata dokona isa pena lao malyiya.  
\v 16 Dopa pipala enda dokome nakamba lamaiyuo, Kiŋi dokona akali dupwame koto kando nyisarimiŋi yuu kyau pingi dulunya papala yuu gii rema yalu pyuo karalapape. Kararaminyipa akali dusipa anda kapu kyuo eparaminyipa nakamba range kata nyuo parambi, leya.   
\p
\v 17 Dokopa akali dolapome enda doko kando lao, Nambwame emba kando pii lalu lao lenge doko minyuo kararamba, leyambi.  
\v 18 Dokona embame dopa pepe. Namwame embena yuu dakena sukusa epo pyao nyela epeyama kande dokopa puu kone dokome windowa kata nambwa pupwa lao nembelene dokona puu pyanyi palyape. Palyapala embena endakinyi rakanepe dee embena kakingi pemalengepe dee embena rakanena ree palu wambu dupwape malu palyuo embena anda dokona petena lare.  
\v 19 Doko kaepala mendali anda doko yaki nyuo nyisa kama epo paramo dokopa pyao kumarami ramo doko baa rangena yulu. Dokona namwana yulu mende daa. Dopa piraminyipape mendali embena anda dokona pisipala randa nyera ramo doko namwana yulu.  
\v 20 Dopa piramopape embame nambwa yalu pyuo epo pelyambano doko wambu dupwa lamairi ramo doko nambwame emba keta lalu lao letambano pii doko minyaro kararamba ingya nara, leyambi.  
\v 21 Dokopa enda baame kapa lapala nakamba pena leya. Dopa pipala enda dokome puu kone doko windowa dokona puu pyanyi palyiya.   
\p
\v 22 Dokopa akali yalu pyuo yuu waa kandala epeyambi dolapo yuu kyau dokona papala yalu piyambi. Dokopa kiŋi dokona akali dupwame yuu wangu dupwana yuu gii rema nakama koteyami. Koteyaminyipape koto kando nyii napala nakama kapu kyuo Jereko epeyami.  
\v 23 Dokopa enakana akali lama dolapo yuu kyau dokona lupyuo epo ipwa yalapala kapu kyuo epo Josua peteyamo dokona peyambi. Papala yulu peparae piyamo dupwa baa lamaiyambi.  
\v 24 Lamaipala dee lao, Kamongo dokome yuu doko peparae namwa jipyamo doko nambwa silyambano. Doko wambu yuu dokona palaminyi dupwa peparaeme namwa kando pakalyaminyi, leyambi.   
\c 3  
\s1 Isaraele Wambu Dupwa Ipwa Jotane //  Yalo Peyami  
\p
\v 1 Yuu gii yangama dokopa Josuamoo dee Isaraele wambu peparaepe wamba sipurapala Akasia dokona palyuo paleyaminyi doko yaki nyepala ipwa Jotane maresa peyami. Papala ipwa Jotane yalo parama lao komau anda pipala isaro kareyami.  
\v 2 Yuu gii rema papeyamopa akali mupwa dupwame wambu paleyaminyi dupwana papyuo dopa lamaiyami.  
\v 3 Purisi dupwame nakamana Kamongo Anatu dokona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko soo wambao paraminyi kandapala dokopa nakamana pinji pyapala komau anda dupwa lalyuo nyepala moko minyuo pupwape.  
\v 4 Nakama wambape dae kamame epa nange kandale dokona purisi dupwame nakama kata lasaka pyuo parami. Dopa piraminyipape Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko soo parami dokona repeta paa nalapape. Mee mende donosale kilomita mendaki dopale ingyuo matarena pupwape, leya.   
\p
\v 5 Dokopa Josuame wambu dupwa dopa lamaiyuo, Rakya Kamongo dokome wambumi yulu pii nange lapo nakama keta piraŋa dokona nakama rapa rapa pyuo poo pyasi ingyuo karalapape, leya.  
\v 6 Lapala baame purisi dupwa lamaiyuo, Wambu dupwa enakana epenaleŋe nakama Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote soo wambo pena leya. Leyamo dokopa nakamame baa leyamuli pyuo peyami.   
\p
\v 7 Dokopa Kamongo dokome Josua lamaiyuo lao, Epapu nambame mende pirunu dokome Isaraele wambu dupwame kando emba akali andakeŋe lao yako lao ketae pyambuo kararami. Dee namba Mosese role kareyo doko suu pyao embapa karambinyi lao soo gisarami.  
\v 8 Dee purisi akali Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote soo parami dupwa lamaiyuo, Nakama ipwa doko kando nyepala dokopa ipwa dokona papala ipwa kee kama repeta pao karena lape, leya.   
\p
\v 9 Dokopa Josuame wambu dupwa lamaiyuo, Dae epapala nakamana Kamongo Anatumi pii mende langira doko selapape.  
\v 10 Nakama parami dokopa baame Kenane wambupi Iti wambupi Ipi wambupi Perasi wambupi Gukasi wambupi Amote wambupi dee Jepusi wambupi dupwa pyao ralinyi nembara.  
\v 11 Kamongo yuu muu peparaena iso karenge dokona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote ipwa Jotane yalo wambo soo peyami kande dokopa Kamongo lete karalu karenge doko nakama pipya karapyalyamo lao soo gisarami.  
\v 12 Dokona epapu Isaraele rara akalisa ipisu lama dusipana akali mendaki mendaki lao rombo palyuo nyelapape.  
\v 13 Purisi akali dupwame Kamongo yuu muu peparaena iso karenge dokona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko soo pao ipwa dokona kimbu kararaminyi dokopa ipwa Jotane doko epa nara. Epa naramopa ipwa doko yuu kyau dopale ingyaro karara, leya.   
\p
\v 14-15 Nenge nenge mandenge yuu gii dokopandeme ipwa doko wakasa paleya.  
\p Dokopa wambu dupwa komau anda pyuo paleyami yuu doko yaki nyepala ipwa doko keno pena peyami. Peyaminyi dokopa purisi dupwa Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko nyepala soo wambo peyami. Dokopa purisi dupwame ipwa dokona moko palyeteyaminyi dokopa ipwa doko soko rali piya.  
\v 16 Dulurename yuu nanesa yuu Atae lenge yuu Saretane repeta singi dokona ipwa doko yuu kyau dopale ingyaro kareya. Dee ipwa lano pao Ipwa Kumungi dokona penge doko soko rali piyamosa wambu dupwa awa pyuo yalo yuu angi Jereko dokona repeta parami ingiya.  
\v 17 Wambu dupwa peparae yuu oo lasi dokona pao kareyaminyipa purisi dupwame Kamongona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko ipwa Jotane dokona sukusa mee yuu oo lasi ingyuo siyamopa sakaro kareyami. Karapala wambu peparae wangu dumarena pao oteyaminyipa purisi dupwa kaeyami.   
\c 4  
\s1 Wambu Dupwame Suu Pyaramiŋi Lao Kana Lapo Ketae Reteyami  
\p
\v 1 Wambu rara peparae Jotane yalo papeyami dokopa Kamongo dokome Josua lamaiyuo,  
\v 2 Rara akalisa ipisu lama dupwana akali mendaki mendaki lao rombo palyuo nyepe.  
\v 3 Nyepala purisi dupwa ipwa Jotane anda suku dokona kareyaminyi panda dokona rolae kana akalisa ipisu lama nyinya lamaipi. Lamaipala kana dupwa nakama nyepala soo epapala nakama rengya kukwa komau anda pyuo palirami dokona isa retena lao lamaipi, leya.   
\p
\v 4 Dokopa akali akalisa ipisu lama Josuame rombo palyiyamo dusipa kee leya. Lapala lao,  
\v 5 Nakamana Kamongo Anatunya Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote soo paraminyi dokona nakama wambo pao Jotane sukusa pupwape. Papala nakama kana mendaki mendaki lao nyepala langena soo ipupwape. Eparaminyi dokopa Isaraele rara peparaena kana mendaki mendaki lao ingyara.  
\v 6 Wambu dupwame kana dusipa kandapa pirami dokopa Kamongo dokome yulu pipyamo doko suu pyapa pirami. Dokona rakyame nakamana wane wanake dupwame kana dupwana lao aki renge palamo lao piso serami.  
\v 7 Piso seraminyi dokopa embame nakama lamaiyuo, Kamongona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko ipwa dokona yalo minyuo peyama dokopa ipwa Jotane doko soko rali piya, lare. Dokona Isaraele wambu dupwame kana dusipa kandapala yuu dakena dopande piyaŋa lao suu pyao kararami, leya.   
\p
\v 8 Akali dupwame Josuame leyamuli pyuo piyami. Kamongome Josua lamaiyamuli pyuo kana akalisa ipisu lama (12) ipwa Jotane dokona sukusa nyiyami. Isaraele rara peparaena suu pyao kana mendaki mendaki lao nyepala soo pao komau anda pyuo paleyami yuu dokona isa reteyami.  
\v 9 Purisi dupwame Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko soo pao ipwa Jotane sukusa kareyaminyi panda dokona Josuame kana akalisa ipisu lama (12) kamameko nyepala isa reteya. (Kana dusipa dakepa mee dokona silyamo.)  
\v 10 Kamongo dokome Josua wambu pinya lena leyamo yulu dupwa pilyamipi lao purisi dupwa ipwa Jotane suku dokona mee isaro kareyami. Doko Moseseme leyamuli pyuo piyami.  
\p Dokopa wambu dupwa waiya lao ipwa doko yalo peyami.  
\v 11 Wambu dupwa peparae ipwa dumarena peyami dokopa purisi akali Kamongona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote siyami dupwa soo wambo peyaminyipa wambu dupwa enakana peyami.  
\v 12 Dokopa akali Urupene rarape Gatena rarape dee akali Manasana rara pingyasipi dupwa Moseseme pinya lao lamaiyamuli pyuo yanda pinya rapa rapa pyuo wambo peyami. Wambu menge dupwa enakana peyami.  
\v 13 Peyaminyi dokopa Kamongona lenge kambu dokona akali taosande akalisa kisima (40,000) yanda pinya rapa rapa pyuo yuu pau lama lama Jereko repeta singi dokona yalo peyami.  
\v 14 Yuu gii dokopa Kamongome yulu piyamo doko Isaraele wambu dupwame kandapala Josua baa akali kamame andake lao soo nyiyami. Nakamame Mosese yako lao banya kingi ketae pyambuo karenge doko suu pyao banya yuu gii kareyamo dusipana nakamame Josua yako lao banya kingi ketae pyambuo kareyami.   
\p
\v 15-16 Dokopa Kamongome Josua lamaiyuo, Purisi dupwame Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko ipwa Jotane sukusa yaki nyuo soo nyisa epena lena leya.  
\v 17 Leyamo dokopa Josuame leyamuli pyuo piyami.  
\v 18 Dokopa purisi dupwa ipwa kee dokona epo kando nyepeyami dokopa ipwa doko yuu mendaki aopa epo papala dee paleyamuli pyuo paleya.   
\p
\v 19 Wambu dupwa kana mupwa dokona pao yuu gii akalisa dokopa ipwa Jotane doko yalo peyami. Papala yuu Jereko neta epenge dorena yuu Gilikale lenge dokona komau anda piyami.  
\v 20 Dokona kana akalisa ipisu lama ipwa Jotane dokona nyiyami dusipa apu rao pisiya.  
\v 21 Baame Isaraele wambu dupwa lamaiyuo, Rakyame nakamana wane wanake dupwame kana dupwana aki renge palase lao piso siyami kande dokopa  
\v 22 ipwa Jotane doko soko rali piyamopa mee yuu oo lasi siyamo dokona Isaraele wambu dupwa kata poko pyao peyaminyi dokona lao lamainya leya.  
\v 23 Nakama lamaiyuo, Nakamana Kamongo Anatu dokome ipwa kota Kone lenge doko soko rali piyamo doko suu pyaoko dee ipwa Jotane doko dopako piyamo dokopa yalo epeyama.  
\v 24 Renge dokona lao isa yuu dakena wambu peparaeme Kamongona porainya renge doko andake wakasaŋa lao soo gisarami. Dee nakamame nakamana Kamongo Anatu doko lakando kingi ketae pyambuo karalu kararami ingilyamo, leya.   
\c 5  
\p
\v 1 Isaraele wambu dupwa ipwa Jotane dokona sukusa kata pena lao ipwa Jotane doko Kamongome soko rali pipya leyami doko yuu Amote wambunya kiŋi ipwa Jotane neta yalyingi dorena karenge peparaepe dee Kenane wambunya kiŋi dupwa peparaeme ipwa kota Metitaraniane lenge kipwa kipwa dokona palenge dupwapeme siyami. Dokona lao Isaraele wambu epelyaminyi lao suu pyao nakama pakapala nakamana porainya renge doko isa peya.   
\s1 Yuu Gilikale Dokona Yanenge Kalomeyami  
\p
\v 2 Dokopa Kamongo dokome Josua lamaiyuo, Kana nenge karenge wakasa lapome wua kema lapo ingyuo wasapala dupwame Isaraele akali dupwa yanenge kalomakaminya leya.  
\v 3 Dokona lao Josuame wua kema lapo wasapala yuu kyau kingi Yanenge Kalomenge lenge dokona nakamana yanenge kalomakamiya.  
\v 4 Isaraele wambu dupwa yuu Isipi yaki nyepala epeyaminyi dokopa wanepe akalipi peparae yanenge kalomo otasi kareyami.  
\v 5 Dopa piyamopape nakama yuu muiyane dokona ee kana akalisa kisima kata pao kareyami dokopa wane dupwa mandeyaminyi dupwa nakamana yanenge kalomakami nayami. Dopa piyamo dokopa Isipi yaki nyuo epeyaminyi  
\v 6 akali kapa yanda piramili dupwame Kamongo kando kamba lao kareyamisa yuu muiyane kata papeyaminyipa peparae kumuo oteyami. Baame akali kumuyaminyi dupwa lamaiyuo, Yuu amenge pingi ee nengepe ando kamonganyi nembenge doko nakama jeroŋo lao nakamana rora ambasu dupwa pipya lalu lao lao lamaiyunu nakama doko kapa kanda narami lao lalu lao leyamuli pyuo piya.  
\v 7 Dokopa nakamana ikinyingi nakamana panda nyiyami dupwa yuu muiyane dokona pao karo yanenge kaloma nayami. Dokona lao Josuame nakamana yanenge kalomakamiya.   
\p
\v 8 Yanenge kalomenge yulu doko otapeyamo dokopa rete dupwa umbwa pilyape lao rara peparae nakamana komau anda pipala paleyami dupwana peteyami.  
\v 9 Dokopa Kamongo dokome Josua kando lao, Nakama Isipi wambunya kendemande ingyuo yulu pyakamyuo kareyamisa elyange renge nyiyami doko epapu nambame nyisa nembakapu. Renge dokona yuu doko kingi Gilikale lenge. Kingi Gilikale lenge doko bange nyisa nembenge dopale.   
\p
\v 10 Isaraele wambu dupwa yuu Gilikale yuu anda lama lama dokona yuu Jereko repeta singi komau anda pyuo palyuo kareyami. Dokopa nakamame kana dokonako yuu gii akalisa ipisu kisima dokona kukwa Nenge Pasopa neyami.  
\v 11 Yuu gii dokopa yangama yuu Kenane dokona nenge andenge lapo kanda soo neyami. Doko witi kisasipi dee nenge borete isi pyambwa nao wasisipi neyami.  
\v 12 Dokopa nenge myana lenge Isaraele wambu dupwa mee maipa piyamo doko Anatumi dee kamba maiya naya. Dokopa nenge yuu Kenane dokona andeyamo dupwa nao palyuo karo piyami.   
\s1 Josua Dee Akali Mende Wua Gela Minyuo Kareyamo Dokopa  
\p
\v 13 Josua baa yuu Jereko dokona repeta karo baame akali mende banya lenge kambu siyamo dorena wua gela minyaro kareyamo doko kandeya. Kandapala dokopa akali baa kareyamo dokona papala dopa lao piso soo, Emba namwana yanda singi dokona mendepe panda namwana yanda pimwaisi? leya.   
\p
\v 14 Leyamo dokopa akali dokome isingi lao, Namba embena yanda singi daa. Dee namba embena yanda pimwai daa. Kamongona ami dokona namba mupwa ingyuo karenge, leya.  
\p Leyamo dokopa Josua baa yuu dokona pangu sepala akali dokona kingi ketae pyambuo lakando lao, Namba embena kendemande yulu pyakange akali. Embame namba apa pyakapili lao suu pilisi? leya.   
\p
\v 15 Leyamo dokopa Kamongona ami dokona mupwa ingyuo karenge dokome Josua kando lamaiyuo, Embena kimbu suu doko nyisa nyepe. Renge dokona lao yuu emba karene doko kamame poo pyasi wakasa, leya. Dopa pinya lao Josua lamaiyamuli pyuo piya.   
\c 6  
\s1 Yuu Jereko Doko Lalyuo Bolombalo Lao Kwaeyo Isa Peya  
\p
\v 1 Isaraele wambu dupwa repeta epeyamisa yuu Jereko dokona kana kame kambu dupwa upi lapala Isaraele dupwa epasaramiŋi lao poraiyuo kando kareyami. Dopa pipala mendali baa yuu taone doko yaki nyuo kama paa nana lao dee mendali kama karo andakare epa nana lao piyami.  
\v 2 Dokopa Kamongo dokome Josua lamaiyuo, Nambame yuu Jerekope dokona kiŋipi yanda singi porai karaminyi dupwape emba keta retelyo.  
\v 3 Dokona yuu gii pakinyamange dusipana yuu peparae yuu mendaki larapu embape embena yanda singi dupwape pipya yuu taone andake doko awali lao maki maki pyuo kimbu pyao piso kata parami.  
\v 4 Purisi akali yanda ipingi wakale wakale bikuli dusipa minyuo nakama Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko soo parami dokona wambo pena. Yuu gii yanda ipingi dokopa purisi dupwame bikuli poo laraminyi dokopa embape embena yanda singi dupwa pipya yuu yanda ipingi nyepo taone andake dokona awali lao maki maki pyuo kimbu pyao piso kata parami.  
\v 5 Dokopa nakamame bikuli pii mende imambu see nao poo londe mende larami. Doko emba aopa sepala dokopa wambu peparaeme pii ketae palyuo laraminyipa yuu taone andake dokona kana kame awali lao karenge doko lalyuo bolombalo lao isa para. Dokopa ami yanda singi peparae yuu taone andake dokona sukusa rolae parami, Kamongome leya.   
\p
\v 6 Leyamo dokopa Josuame purisi dusipa kee lao dopa leya. Nakamame Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko nyelapape. Nyepala akali yanda ipingi nyepo dusipame bikuli minyuo wambo pupwape.  
\v 7 Lapala dokopa baame akali dupwa lamaiyuo, Yuu taone andake dokona awali lao kanda soo maki maki pyuo kimbu pyao piso pena leya. Kamongona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote soo parami dokona yanda singi lapo wambo iso pena leya.   
\p
\v 8 Dokopa nakamame Josua lamaiyamuli pyuo piyami. Yanda singi lapo kamame wambo peyami. Peyaminyi dokopa purisi akali yanda ipingi nyepo dusipame bikuli poo lao peyami.  
\v 9 Dokopa dee purisi akali wakale lapome Kamongona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko soo peyami. Kamame enakana yanda singi lapoko peyami. Dopa pyuo peyaminyi dokopa bikuli poo lao peyami.  
\v 10 Dopa piyaminyipape Josuame banya akali dupwa lamaiyuo, Pii poraiyuo laa nana dee isa isa pii kuki mendepe laa nana ama daa, leya. Nambame langirunu dokopa nakamame kapa larami, leya.  
\v 11 Dokona lao baame purisi dupwa lamaiyuo, Kamongona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko nyepala soo yuu mendaki yuu taone andake dokona awali lena leya. Leyamo dokopa nakama dopa pipala komau anda pyuo paleyami dokona dee kamba kapu kyuo epapala kukwa dokopa paleyami.   
\p
\v 12-13 Yuu gii dokopa yangama wamba kukwa Josua baa sipureyamo dokopa yuu lapo ingyuo banya yanda singi lapo yuu taone doko awali lao wambo peyaminyi dokopa purisi akali yanda ipingi nyepo dusipame enakana bikuli poo lao peyami. Peyaminyi dokopa dee purisi akali wakale lapome Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko soo peyami. Kamame enakana yanda singi lapo peyami. Dopa pyuo peyaminyi dokopa bikuli poo lao peyami.  
\v 14 Yuu gii lapo dokona nakama yuu taone andake dokona kamba yuu mendaki awali lao maki maki pyuo kimbu pyao piso papala nakama kapu kyuo komau anda paleyami yuu dokona dee epeyami. Nakama yuu gii pakinyamange nembo mee dopako pyuo kareyami.  
\v 15 Yuu gii yanda ipingi dokopa nakama yango rali piyamo sipuro papala wambo piyami dopaleko ingyuo yuu taone andake doko awali lao yuu yanda ipingiko maki maki pyuo kimbu pyao piso kata peyami. Yuu gii doko iki yuu yanda ipingi dopa piyami.  
\v 16 Yuu yanda ipingi awali leyami dokopa purisi dupwame bikuli pii repeta lalana piyami. Dokopa Josua banya akali dupwa pii poraiyuo lena leya. Lapala baame lao, Kamongo dokome yuu taone andake doko nakama jipya, leya.  
\v 17 Yuu taone andake dokope bange peparae singi dupwape yaka lao pyao kokwa soo nembarami. Dopa pyuo nakamame Anatu bange maingi doko suu pyao pirami. Dopa pipala namwana akali lama yuu dake waa kandala epeyambinyi dokopa pamuku enda Oreapa nakamba yalu pyuo pisiyamo doko dee banya ree palu dokope yaki nyuo kaeyarami.  
\v 18 Dopa pipalape bange pyao kokwa soo nembaraminyi dupwana mende nyii nalapape. Doko daaŋa lapala nyerami ramo doko Isaraele wambu dupwa koo keta pao randa andake nyerami.  
\v 19 Bange peparae kana kulingipi kana golope kone kanape anepe dusipame wasisi dupwa peparae Kamongona lao liti pyuo retarami. Kamongona kana retenge dokona retarami.\fig Nakama pii poraiyuo kaeyo leyaminyipa kana kame awali lao paleyamodoko lalyuo bolombalo lao isa peya.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="6:20" \fig*   
\p
\v 20 Dokona lao purisi dupwame bikuli poo leyami dokopa akali dupwame aopa sepala nakama pii poraiyuo kaeyo leyaminyipa kana kame awali lao paleyamo doko lalyuo bolombalo lao isa peya. Dokopa yanda singi dupwa yuu kyau dokona pulyuo papala yuu taone andake dokona sukusa rolae pao yuu doko nyiyami.  
\v 21 Nyepala nakamana wua gela dupwame yuu dokona wambu peparae peteyami dupwa piyami. Enda akalipi endemo alemope dee mapwae parangepe dupwa pyao kumakayami. Nakamame mena sipisipi mena dongepe mena bulamakaope dupwa peparae pyao kumakayami.   
\p
\v 22 Dokopa Josuame akali lama yuu yalu pyuo waa kandala peyambinyi dolapo lamaiyuo, Nakambame baa kando lalu lao lao lamaiyambinyili pyuo enda pamuku dokona anda papala baape banya ree palu dupwape nyuo minyuo nyisa ipupwape, leya.  
\v 23 Dokopa nakamba papala enda Oreapa banya endangi rakangepa dee banya pemalenge dupwape dee banya ree palu dupwa pipya nyuo minyuo nyisa epeyambi. Nakamba wambu ree palupi dee kendemande wambupi dupwa peparae lete kararami lao Isaraele wambu komau anda pyuo paleyami dokona repeta minyuo epo pisiyami.  
\v 24 Dokopa enakana nakama yuu taone andake doko isare palyiyamisa rao yuu minyiya. Dokona bange siyamo dupwa role pyapeta reya. Reyamopape bange kana golope kana kulingipi kone kanape anepe dusipame wasingi dupwa nakamame nyepala Kamongona kana retenge dokona reteyami.  
\v 25 Dopa piyamopape Josuame akali lama yalu pyuo yuu Jereko doko waa kandala pena leyamo dokopa pamuku enda Oreapa dokome nyuo yalu pyuo pisiyamo dokona Josuame baape banya ree palu dupwape lete wai pyao nyiya. Banya para pyasi dupwa yuu Isaraele dokona karo yuu gii dakepa palu karaminyi.   
\p
\v 26 Yuu gii dokopa Josuame repe repe pii lamaikondali pyuo lao, Wambu mendeme yuu taone Jereko dake kamba pira ramo doko Kamongome baa koo keta pisara. Dokona lao mendeme anda dokona pinya suu pyao kana susa retaramo dokona ikinyingi mupwa doko kumara. Dee mendeme kana kame kambu dupwa wasera ramo dokona ikinyingi enakana mandenge doko kumara.   
\p
\v 27 Dokona lao Kamongo doko Josuapa role pyao kareyambisa banya kingi doko yuu muu dupwana raeyo soo kapa kapa piyami.   
\s3 7:1—9:27 Josua baame Isaraele yanda singi dupwa iso kareyamopa nakama yuu Kenane dokona yuu kyau karenge dokona papala taone andake kingi Eyai lenge doko pyao nyepala Gipione range wambu dupwa pipya pii mendakinya palyuo lao kareyami.  
\c 10  
\s1 Isaraele Wambu Dupwame Amote Wambu Dupwa Pyao Raliyami  
\p
\v 1 Josuame yuu taone Jereko pyao kokwa soo dee yuu dokona kiŋi pyao kokwa soo piya. Dopa pipala yuu Eyai dokona dopako pyuo piyamo doko leyaminyi Jerusaleme range kiŋi banya kingi Atoniseteke lenge dokome siya. Sepala Gipione wambu dupwame mona siyamopa Isaraele wambu dupwa pipya manda rao peteyami doko leyaminyi siyako.  
\v 2 Dokona lao Jerusaleme wambu dupwa ama pakayami. Renge dokona lao yuu taone wakale wakale kiŋi iso kareyaminyi dupwa yuu Gipione doko andake dopale. Yuu Eyai doko mee taone kuki iki. Dee yuu Gipione range yanda singi dupwame yanda poraiyuo pingi.  
\v 3 Dokona lao akali Atonisetekeme pii nembo akali Oyame yuu Eperonena kiŋi dokope akali Pirame yuu Jamurana kiŋi dokope akali Japia yuu Lakisinya kiŋi dokope dee akali Depa yuu Ekelonena kiŋi dokope dopa lamaiya.  
\v 4 Gipione range wambu dupwame Josuamoo Isaraele wambu dupwa pipya mona sipyamopa puu minyuo pisiminyi dokona nakama dae epapala nambamoo pipya Gipione range wambu dupwa yanda pyuo pyamanale, leya.  
\v 5 Amote kiŋi kingi paki dusipame Jerusaleme range kiŋi dokope Eperone range kiŋi dokope Jamura range kiŋi dokope Lakisi dee Ekelone range kiŋi dolapope nakamana yanda singi dupwa peparae nyuo malu palyuo yuu Gipione doko awali lao karo yanda piyami.   
\p
\v 6 Dokopa Gipione range dupwame Josua yuu Gilikale paleyamo dokona pii wai nembo leyami. Embame namwa yaki nyii napipi. Emba waiya lao aopa epo namwa nyiso lete wai pyao nyelase. Amote kiŋi yuu kyau dupwana palenge dupwa peparaeme malu palyapala namwa pyala epelyaminyi, leyami.   
\p
\v 7 Leyaminyi doko sepala Josua banya yanda singi peparae dupwa pipya yuu Gilikale yaki nyepala nyisala peyami.  
\v 8 Peyaminyi dokopa Kamongome Josua lamaiyuo, Ama paka napipi. Wambu dupwana mendeme emba pyao isa palya narami. Nambana porainya renge dokome embame wambu dupwa nyuo anamasi minyare, leya.  
\v 9 Leyamo dokopa Josua dee banya yanda singi dupwape kukwa yuu Gilikale dokona karo yuu Gipione peyami. Papala Amote wambu dupwa rapa rapa pii nayaminyipa nakamame wambu dupwa walu lao piyami.  
\v 10 Amote wambu dupwame Isaraele yanda singi dupwa epeyaminyi kandeyaminyi dokopa Kamongome nakama pakanyi pyambuya. Pyambuyamo dokopa Isaraele wambu dupwame Amote wambu yuu Gipione dokona pyapala yuu Beterome kyau kata kuki mendena pyao lano ralinyi nembeyami. Ralinyi nembo pao yuu Aseka dee Maketa yuu donorena singi dokona pyambuyami.  
\v 11 Isaraele wambu dupwame peteta peyaminyi dokopa Amote wambu dupwa lano makando peyaminyipa Kamongome yake dokona piso randake kapa isa peyapala wambu malumee pyao kumakaya. Isaraele wambu dupwame wambu pyao kumakayaminyipape randake kapame kamame wakasa pyao kumakaya.   
\p
\v 12 Kamongo dokome Isaraele akali dupwa nyisiyamopa Amote akali dupwa pyao wini piyami. Yuu gii dokopa Josuame Kamongo pii lamaiya. Baame Isaraele wambunya lenge kambu dokona dopa leya. Neta, yuu Gipione kanda kanda dokona mee rao kara. Kana, yuu Ainjalone rapu dorena kanda kanda mee rao kara.  
\v 13 Isaraele wambu dupwame ene wini pinya piyaminyi dokopa neta kanape dolapo mee romo pii nao rao karalu kareyambi. Dopa piyamo dokopa yake suku dokona neta mee rao karalu kareya. Dopa piyamo dokopa yuu yangama piso pao yuu kukwa opetaeko rao karalu kareya. Dopa piyaŋa lao Akali Rolae Pingi Dupwana Buku dokona pyasi palamo.  
\v 14 Yuu wamba kanda soo dokopa piso pao epapupi yulu dopale pyuo Kamongome mee akalinya pii mendepe warombo see nange. Isaraele wambu dupwame yanda pyuo kareyaminyipa Kamongome nakama poraiyuo nyiso kareyamo piyami.   
\p
\v 15 Enakana dokopa Josuamoo banya yanda singi dupwa pipya nakama paleyaminyi yuu Gilikale dokona dee kapu kyuo peyami.   
\s3 10:16—23:16 Nakamame yuu Kenane doko pyao nyuo anamasi minyiyami. Dopa pipala yuu doko Isaraele rara dupwa liti pyuo nyiyami.  
\c 24  
\s1 Josuame Yuu Sikeme Dokona Isaraele Wambu Dupwa Pii Lamaiya  
\p
\v 1 Josuame Isaraele rara dupwa peparae kyakale lao nyuo yuu Sikeme dokona malu palyiya. Baame akali kyawape akali mupwa ingyuo karengepe jasi akalipi Isaraele wambunya iso karengepe dupwa peparae epena lao kyakale leyamo dokopa wambu dupwa peparae Anatunya lenge kambu siyamo dokona epo kareyami.  
\v 2 Dokopa Josuame wambu dupwa peparae kando lamaiyuo, Kamongo Isaraele wambunya Anatu dokome pii dake dopa letamo, leya. Ama yuu wamba nakamana rora ambasu dupwa ipwa Yuporisa wangu pakirename kareyaminyi dokopa bange wakale anatuŋu lao lakando kareyami. Nakamana rora amabasu dupwana akali mendaki baa Tera lenge doko Aporakamepa Nayopana rakange.  
\v 3 Yuu gii dokopa nakamana kauwange Aporakame ipwa Yuporisa wangu pakirename kareyamopa nambame nyuo lanyuo yuu Kenane peparae dokona sukusa mondo lao laminyuo peyo. Papala dokopa banya para pyasi ree palu andake inginyi pyambuyu.  
\v 4 Nambame baa wane Aisake maiyu. Maipala nambame dee Aisake keta Jekope Isopa maiyu. Dee yuu kyau kuki pingi singi yuu Itome lenge doko Iso banya yuu inginya lao maiyu. Dopa piyunupape nakamana rora ambasu Jekope lenge banya wane wanakepe dupwa pipya yuu Isipi dokona lano peyami.  
\v 5 Dokopa enakana nambame Mosese Eronepa mapanyi peyapala yuu Isipi keta randa andake pena leyo. Dopa leyonopape nambame nakama nyisa nyiyu.  
\v 6 Nakamana rora ambasu dupwa yuu Isipi kareyaminyipa nambame neta nyuo lanyuo epeyo. Lanyuo epeyonopa Isipi range wambu dupwame mena matana pisope dee mena oseme ipyuo penge uliuli dupwana piso pyao peta ralyuo nyela epeyami.  
\v 7 Epeyaminyi dokopa nakamana rora ambasu dupwa ipwa kota Kone lenge dokona kando nyepala namba keta ateŋa lao kandokondali pyuo nyisinya lao piso soo leyami. Leyaminyi dokopa nambame Isaraele wambupi Isipi wambupi dupwana kanya dokona liti pyuo yuu doko iminjanyi pyambuyu. Pyambwapala nambame Isipi range dupwa ipwa kota dokome nyuo yambe pyapala ipwame nena leyo. Nambame Isipi wambu dupwa keta yulu piyu doko nakama soo nyilyaminyi.  
\p Nakama yuu muiyane dokona ee kana malu mee nembo paleyami.  
\v 8 Ipwa Jotane yuu neta pyakayo epenge dorena Amote wambu palenge dokona nakama nyuo lanyuo epeyo. Epeyo dokopa wambu dupwame nakama piyaminyipape nambame nakama nyisiyunusa wambu dupwa nyuo pyao anamasi minyiyami. Nakama pao kareyaminyipa nambame doloma pyao kokwa siyunusa nakamame nakambana yuu doko nyiyami.  
\v 9 Dee yuu Moape dokona kiŋi akali Beleke Sipona ikinyingi dokome nakama piya. Baame Biona ikinyingi Belame kareyamo dokona pii nembo piso soo nakama keta randa palena lakana leya.  
\v 10 Dopa piyamopape nambame Belameme pii leyamo doko sakame napuli lao suu piyu dokona baame nakama keta elyape pisiya. Dokona lao nambame nakama Beleke keta kingi raka lao nyiyu.   
\p
\v 11 Dokopa nakama Jotane oko soo Jereko epeyami dokopa Jereko range akali dupwame nakama piyami. Dokopa Amote wambupi Perisi wambupi Kenane wambupi Iti wambupi Gukasi wambupi Ipi wambupi dee Jepusi wambupi dupwa peparaeme nakama yanda pyuo kareyaminyipape nambana porainya renge dokome nakama anamasi minyiyami.  
\v 12 Nakama epeyaminyi dokopa namba wambo pao wambu dupwa pakanyi andake pyambuyu. Dopa pyuo nakamame Amote kiŋi lama pyao raliyaminyisa piya. Nakamana yandape wua gelape dupwame mendali piyaminde daa.  
\v 13 Nambame yuu mendena nakamame mende yulu pyuo wara pii nange dokope dee taone nakamame waso pii nayami dupwape nyuo jiyu. Dokona lao epapu dakepa nakama yuu dokona karapala isa girapo olipipi dupwa nakamame wara pii nayami dupwana jingi lyuo nao palaminyi, Kamongome dopa letamo lao Josuame leya.   
\p
\v 14 Dopa lapala Josua pii konda pyuo leya. Epapu dakepa Kamongo doko rape rape lao banya yulu rolae pyakamyuo yaki nyii nalapape. Nakamana rora ambasu dupwa yuu Mesopotemia dee yuu Isipi dokona bange wakale anatuŋu lao lakandeyami dupwa nyuo nembalapape. Nembapala nakamame Kamongona yulu iki pyakamilapape.  
\v 15 Dokona lao nakamame Kamongona yulu dokona pinya lao suu pyaa narami ramo nakamame mendena yulu pyakamirami lao suu piyami kande doko dakepa rombo palyuo lalapape. Nakamana rora ambasu dupwa yuu Mesopotemia dokona karo bange wakale anatuŋu lao lakandeyami dupwape panda yuu Amote karaminyi dokona wambunya anatu wakale dupwana lao rombo palyuo lalapape. Dopa piraminyipape nambamoo nambana ree palu dupwape Kamongona yulu pyakamirama, leya.   
\p
\v 16 Leyamo dokopa wambu dupwame isingi lao, Kamongo Anatu yaki nyii napala anatu menge dupwana yulu pyakami narama ingilyamo, leyami.  
\v 17 Lapala namwana Kamongo Anatu dokome namwana rakange dupwape namwape yuu Isipi dokona kendemande yulu pyakamyuo kareyamano dokopa neta nyuo lanyuo epeya. Epeyamo dokopa yulu andake piyamo dupwa namwame kandeyama. Namwa panya peyamano dupwana akali rara wakale wakale dupwame namwa pyalana piyaminyipape Anatumi namwa nyuo retaro karo nyiso lanyuo peya.  
\v 18 Namwa epeyama dokopa namwana Kamongo Anatu dokome Amote wambu yuu dakena palenge dupwa pyao ralinyi nembakaya. Nembakayamo dokona lao namwa opetae Kamongona yulu pyakamirama. Baa namwana Anatu, leyami.   
\p
\v 19 Leyaminyi dokopa Josuame wambu dupwa kando dopa lamaiyuo, Nakamame Kamongona yulu kapa pyakami narami ingilyamo rapisi. Baa Anatu poo pyasi wakasa dokome kyambo anatu dupwa lakanda narami lao suu pilyamo. Baame nakamana koo dupwa nyuo kame saka nara ingilyamo.  
\v 20 Dee mende nakamame Anatu yaki nyepala rara wakalena kyambo anatu lenge dupwana yulu pyakamyuo kararami ramo Anatu baame nakamana yanda pimwai ingyuo randa joo pira. Wamba baame nakama keta elyape ingyuo pisiyamopape epapu baame nakama pyao kokwa sera, leya.   
\p
\v 21 Leyamo dokopa wambu dupwame Josua lamaiyuo, Doko daa. Namwame Kamongona yulu pyakamirama, leyami.   
\p
\v 22 Leyami dokopa Josuame isingi lamaiyuo, Kamongona yulu pirama lao nakama range lalu lao lao karaminyi, leya. Leyamo dokopa nakamame dopa lao, Kinyi. Namwa rangeme lalu lao letamano, leyami.   
\p
\v 23 Leyaminyipa Josuame lamaiyuo, Nakamame pii doo letaminyi dokona rara wakalena kyambo anatu nyisa nembapala Kamongo Isaraele wambunya Anatu doko iki yapalyepala mona kapu kyuo maipwape, leya.   
\p
\v 24 Leyamo dokopa wambu dupwame Josua kando isingi lao, Namwana Kamongo Anatunya yulu pyakamyuo banya pii dupwa laramuli pyuo warombo soo kararama, leyami.   
\p
\v 25 Leyaminyi dokona Josuame kana minyuo lalu lao lenge pii wambu dupwana lao pyao palyiya. Pyao palyapala yuu Sikeme dokona baame nakamame mawa piipi mana piipi minyuo pyuo kararami lao maiya.  
\v 26 Maipala Josuame mawa pii dupwa buku Anatunya lowa pii pyasi palenge dokona pyao reteya. Retapala kana andake mende nyepala Kamongona misi lenge panda dokona isa oke lenge kareyamo renge dokona reteya.   
\p
\v 27 Retapala Josuame wambu dupwa lamaiyuo, Kamongome namwa pii langipyamo dupwa peparae kana dakeme sipyamosa namwame yuu peparae kana kandapala kana minyuo lalu lao lenge pii dokona lao suu pyarama. Suu pyapala kana dokome lasaka pili lao nakamame namwana Anatu baa kando kamba laa naramisa pira ingilyamo, leya.  
\v 28 Lapala dokopa Josuame wambu peparae dupwa nakama rangena yuu wakale wakale dupwana pena leyamopa peyami.   
\s1 Josuapa Eliasapa Kumuyambi  
\p
\v 29 Enakana Josua Nanena ikinyingi baa Kamongona kendemande akali ee kana andete mendaki dee akalisa mendaki (110) nembo karapala kumuya.  
\v 30 Kumuyamo dokopa nakamame banya yuu angi dokona yuu Timinate Sera lenge dokona malu piyami. Yuu kyau kingi Gasi lenge dulurena yuu Eporaime kyau pyalya pyana pingi dokona malu piyami.   
\p
\v 31 Josua baa lete kareyamopa Isaraele wambu dupwame Kamongona yulu pyakamyuo kareyami. Dopa pyuo karapala Josua kumapeyamo dokopa Kamongona yulu pyuoko kareyami. Karapala nakamana akali kyawa ingyuo karenge Kamongo banya wambu dupwana lao yulu andake pyakamiyamo dupwa rangeme kandeyaminyi dupwa lete kareyaminyi dokopa Kamongona yulu pyuo kareyamiko.   
\p
\v 32 Isaraele wambu dupwa yuu Isipi yaki nyuo epeyaminyi dokopa Josepena kuli yeelyo minyuo epapala yuu Sikeme dokona malu piyami. Yuu malu piyaminyi doko akali Jekope baame Amo yuu Sikeme dokona rakange ingyuo kareyamo dokona ikinyingi dupwa kana kulingi andete mendaki (100) dokome ropo pyao nyiyamo doko Josepena para pyasi wambu dupwana ingyuo nyiyami.   
\p
\v 33 Eliasa Eronena ikinyingi kumuyamo dokopa banya ikinyingi Pineyasena yuu Gipia dokona malu piyami. Yuu taone Gipia doko yuu Eporaime kyau kuki pingi singi dokona siya.   